"title": "8271: holiness, purpose of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8271",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God in his holiness desires a holy people amongst whom he can dwell, and who can effectively worship, witness to and serve him as they prepare for a future with God and to be like God.</p>\n<h2>The goal of holiness is to be like God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:2\">LEV 19:2</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:48\">MAT 5:48</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:29\">ROM 8:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:10\">HEB 12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:15-1Pet1:16\">1PE 1:15–1:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:2-1John3:3\">1JN 3:2–3:3</a></p>\n<h2>God dwells with holy people</h2>\n<h3>God dwelt with the people of Israel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut23:14\">DEU 23:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:42-Exod29:46\">EXO 29:42–29:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num5:1-Num5:3\">NUM 5:1–5:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs9:3\">1KI 9:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:26-Ezek37:28\">EZK 37:26–37:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech2:10-Zech2:12\">ZEC 2:10–2:12</a></p>\n<h3>God dwells with Christians</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:19-Eph2:22\">EPH 2:19–2:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:16-1Cor3:17\">1CO 3:16–3:17</a></p>\n<h2>Holiness is required for acceptable worship</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:19-Heb10:22\">HEB 10:19–10:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev22:17-Lev22:22\">LEV 22:17–22:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr29:15-2Chr29:31\">2CH 29:15–29:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa56:6-Isa56:7\">ISA 56:6–56:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:7-Matt15:9\">MAT 15:7–15:9</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:6\">MRK 7:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:13\">ISA 29:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1\">ROM 12:1</a></p>\n<h2>Holiness is needed for effective witness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:9-1Pet2:12\">1PE 2:9–2:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:41\">EZK 20:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:20\">EZK 36:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek39:7\">EZK 39:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:1-1Pet3:2\">1PE 3:1–3:2</a></p>\n<h2>Holiness is needed for godly service</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:13-Heb9:14\">HEB 9:13–9:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:41\">EXO 28:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev21:6-Lev21:8\">LEV 21:6–21:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr35:3\">2CH 35:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:9\">ZEP 3:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:74-Luke1:75\">LUK 1:74–1:75</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:20-2Tim2:21\">2TI 2:20–2:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:14\">TIT 2:14</a></p>\n<h2>Holiness leads to a future hope</h2>\n<h3>Holy people will see God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:14\">HEB 12:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:8\">MAT 5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:13\">1TH 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:10\">2TH 1:10</a></p>\n<h3>Holy people will receive eternal life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:22\">ROM 6:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:11\">2PE 3:11</a></p>\n<h3>Holy people will inherit the kingdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:12\">COL 1:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:18\">DAN 7:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:22\">DAN 7:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:27\">DAN 7:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:18\">EPH 1:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:6\">REV 20:6</a></p>\n<h3>Holy people will judge the world</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:2\">1CO 6:2</a></p>\n<h3>Believers' ultimate destiny is to share God's holiness for ever</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:25-Eph5:27\">EPH 5:25–5:27</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:2-Rev21:3\">REV 21:2–21:3</a></strong></p>",
